description: You can use various circle characters and brackets like ( and ) or ꒰ and ꒱ to make thought bubbles for your thinking emotes. Go ahead and fill in what they are thinking about with words, objects, or even another emoticon ;). This is also a good way to show a sleeping emoticon is dreaming.
